<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>530 and DT-466/408 Diesel Engine Service (1994) - ROCKER ARM ASSEMBLY, CAMSHAFT, TAPPETS AND PUSH RODS -
        ROCKER ARM ASSEMBLY
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>ROCKER ARM ASSEMBLY</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="1">
            <title>REMOVAL</title>
            <para>Remove the crankcase breather tube. Refer to the appropriate manual section for removal procedures.
            </para>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Remove valve lever (rocker arm) assembly as follows: (Refer to
                    <emph type="bold">Figure
                        <hotlnk xrefid="ef1050502">5.2</hotlnk>
                    </emph>
                    ).
                </para>
                <step2>
                    <para count="1">Loosen valve lever (rocker arm) adjusting screw nuts to loosen adjusting screw 1/2
                        turn.
                    </para>
                    <specpara>
                        <note>
                            <para>Loosening valve lever (rocker arm) adjusting screw 1/2 turn will avoid possible valve
                                train damage during installation.
                            </para>
                        </note>
                    </specpara>
                </step2>
                <step2>
                    <para count="1">Loosen valve lever (rocker arm) bracket bolts (long cylinder head bolts).</para>
                </step2>
                <step2>
                    <para count="1">Lift valve lever (rocker arm) assembly from the cylinder head.</para>
                </step2>
                <step2>
                    <para count="1">Remove six long bolts and washers from valve lever (rocker arm) assembly and set
                        aside.
                    </para>
                    <specpara>
                        <important>
                            <para>AT THIS STAGE OF DISASSEMBLY, MEASURE CAMSHAFT LOBE LIFT.</para>
                        </important>
                    </specpara>
                    <figure id="ef1050502" figsize="col-wide">
                        <graphic id="eg2316" filename="../figeg2/EG2316.webp" type="webp"/>
                        <caption>Figure 5.2.</caption>
                        <calloutgroup>
                            <callout1>1. Rocker Shaft Bracket</callout1>
                            <callout1>2. Cylinder Head</callout1>
                        </calloutgroup>
                    </figure>
                </step2>
            </step1>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
